  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/lang-styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <article>
      <section class="fade-in">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Latest Malayalam OTT Movies</h2>
        <div class="movie-grid">
          <% malMovies.forEach(movie => { %>
            <div class="card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Movie" aria-label="Details for <%= movie.title %>">
              <figure>
                <img src="<%= movie.poster %>" alt="<%= movie.title %> Malayalam OTT release poster" itemprop="image" loading="lazy">
              </figure>
              <h3 itemprop="name"><%= movie.title %></h3>
              <p><strong>Release Date:</strong> <span itemprop="datePublished"><%= movie.releaseDate %></span></p>
              <div itemprop="actor" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
                <p><strong>Cast:</strong> <span itemprop="name"><%= movie.cast %></span></p>
              </div>
              <div itemprop="director" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
                <p><strong>Crew:</strong> <span itemprop="name"><%= movie.crew %></span></p>
              </div>
              <p itemprop="description"><strong>Plot:</strong> <%= movie.plot %></p>
              <p><strong>OTT Platform:</strong> <span itemprop="provider"><%= movie.platform %></span></p>
              <meta itemprop="genre" content="Malayalam Cinema">
              <meta itemprop="url" content="https://ihalokam.vercel.app/movies/<%= movie.title.replace(/\s+/g, '-') %>">
            </div>
          <% }); %>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="fade-in">
        <p>The Malayalam film industry continues to shine in 2025 with its latest OTT releases, offering a rich blend of popular hits, anticipated upcoming films, and captivating dubbed movies. Available on platforms like Netflix, Amazon Prime, Disney+ Hotstar, and Manorama Max, the latest Malayalam OTT movies cater to diverse tastes. Here are six key aspects of these releases, highlighting why they’re a must-watch.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="fade-in">
        <h2>1. Popular Hits Dominating Latest Malayalam OTT Releases</h2>
        <p>The latest Malayalam OTT releases feature blockbuster hits that have enthralled audiences. <em>L2: Empuraan</em>, the sequel to <em>Lucifer</em>, starring Mohanlal, is a standout action thriller now streaming on Disney+ Hotstar, grossing over ₹260 crore worldwide. Another gem, <em>Marco</em>, an action-packed film with Unni Mukundan, has transitioned from theaters to SonyLIV, captivating fans with its gritty narrative. These latest Malayalam OTT movies showcase Mollywood’s knack for gripping storytelling.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="fade-in">
        <h2>2. Exciting Upcoming Malayalam OTT Releases in 2025</h2>
        <p>Anticipation is high for upcoming Malayalam OTT release movies slated for 2025. <em>Oshana</em>, a suspenseful tale of folklore and mystery, is set to debut on Manorama Max in January 2025. Another awaited title, <em>Kaaliyan</em>, a period drama featuring Prithviraj Sukumaran, promises a historical epic on OTT platforms later this year. These upcoming releases ensure the latest Malayalam OTT films remain a hot topic.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="fade-in">
        <h2>3. Malayalam Dubbed Movies Adding Variety</h2>
        <p>Malayalam dubbed movies are expanding the appeal of the latest Malayalam OTT releases. <em>Meiyazhagan</em>, a Tamil film dubbed in Malayalam, starring Karthi and Arvind Swamy, is a heartwarming drama available on Netflix since October 2024. Similarly, <em>Brinda</em>, a Telugu crime thriller dubbed in Malayalam, featuring Trisha, has gained traction on JioHotstar. These dubbed films enrich the latest Malayalam OTT movies catalog, offering diverse storytelling to viewers.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="fade-in">
        <h2>4. Genre Diversity in Latest Malayalam OTT Movies</h2>
        <p>The latest Malayalam OTT releases in 2025 offer a vibrant mix of genres. Romantic comedies like <em>Painkili</em>, streaming on Manorama Max, deliver laughs with Sajin Gopu and Anaswara Rajan, while thrillers like <em>Officer on Duty</em> on Netflix, starring Kunchacko Boban, keep viewers on edge. Dramas such as <em>Thudarum</em> on JioHotstar explore emotional depth, ensuring the latest Malayalam OTT films appeal to all.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="fade-in">
        <h2>5. Spotlight on New and Veteran Talent</h2>
        <p>The latest Malayalam OTT release movies highlight both emerging and veteran talent. New directors like Sreeraj Sreenivasan, with <em>Pravinkoodu Shappu</em> on SonyLIV, blend dark comedy and suspense, while stars like Mohanlal and Mammootty shine in films like <em>Barroz</em> on Disney+ Hotstar. Young actors like Tovino Thomas in <em>Identity</em> add fresh energy, making these latest Malayalam OTT releases a talent showcase.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="fade-in">
        <h2>6. How to Catch the Latest Malayalam OTT Releases This Week</h2>
        <p>Staying updated on the latest Malayalam OTT releases this week is simple. Platforms like Netflix and SonyLIV announce new titles, such as <em>Maranamass</em>, a dark comedy streaming on SonyLIV from May 14, 2025. Following X posts from @OTT_Trackers or subscribing to OTT newsletters ensures you catch films like <em>Good Bad Ugly</em> on Netflix. The latest Malayalam OTT movies are just a click away.</p>
      </section>

